Mexico ' s dollar CCP rate falls in October . Mexico ' s dollar CCP rate fell three basis points in October from the previous month to 7 . 05 percent , the Banco de Mexico said . The central bank said that the CCP , the average bank term desposit cost measured in dollars in Mexican banks , was 7 . 08 percent in September . - - Mexico City newsroom + 525 728 - 7902 
